title: Kylie Jenner puts on a busty display in white underthings | Daily Mail Online
text: Share this article Share The social media sensation paired her chesty white tank top with what appeared to be a pair of white boxer briefs with Cyrillic text across the hip-hugging waistband. Snapping up a storm: The teen stunner contrasted her sexy selfie with some cute and low-key Snapchat pics where she wore the playful bunny filter Although the sexy pose was typically Kylie, the makeup mogul switched up her style a bit with a new hairstyle. The better half of Tyga changed her tresses to sport long fringe besides her cascading raven locks. In the pic, you can see the reality teen complimenting her hair with long red nails while she flashes a neutral face at the camera. The magic of makeup: Earlier on Snapchat, the makeup mogul showed off her impressive collection of cosmetics housed in her temporary 'glam room' Her favorites: The social media sensation gave her fans an intimate peek of her favorite brands and products, giving a shoutout to NARS concealer and a Anastasia Beverly Hills eyeshadow palette in her Snap story It seems glamour is the name of the game if you're Kylie. Earlier today the celeb took to Snapchat to show off her enviable makeup room. It was no surprise that the Kylie Cosmetics entrepreneur was stocked with a serious makeup collection, but the Keeping Up With The Kardashians talent did explain that this spot was only temporary. Right now the stylist star is putting the finishing touches on her permanent 'glam room' which will be complete with a custom lip shaped couch, pink marble and 'everything pink and girly and super Barbie,' according Kylie. The star finished her Snaps by telling fans 'I can't wait to show you guys when it's all done.' Share or comment on this article 5
